content.rendered:
Directed by Trinadha Rao Nakkina.

Written by Prasanna Kumar Bezawada. Trinadha Rao Nakkina. Prasanna Kumar Bezawada. Sai Krishna Biyyapu.

Cast Ram Pothineni(Sanju). Anupama Parameswaran(Anupama (as Anupama Parameshwaran)). Pranitha(Reethu). Prakash Raj(Viswanath). Aamani(Lakshmi). Sithara(Gayatri). V. Jayaprakash(Sanju’s father). Krishna Murali Posani(Sanju’s uncle). Suresh(Reethu’s father). Sayaji Shinde(Karthik’s father). Ram Prasad(Sanju’s friend). Praveen(Mechanic). Sapthagiri(Auto Driver) .Mahesh Achanta.Avinash.Basha.Jayaprakash.Kalpana.Kamalika.Mirchi Kiran.Ravi Kiran.Lakshmi Ravi Kundana.Monisha. Kamal Teja Narla(Sanju Office Colleague).Satti Pandu. Pkaushikji(Prem).Tulasi Ram.Ravi.Santhosh.Santhoshi.Sathya.Sathyasri. Satya(Sanju’s friend). Noel Sean(Karthik).Shravani.Srinivas.Surya.Teja.Vinay.Yadamaraju

Language Telugu.

Producers Lakshman. Dil Raju. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh.

Production Sri Venkateswara Creation.
